Doc: Upon the occurrence of an Abandonment of Scheme, as defined in clause (h)(iv) of the Emissions Annex, one of the following elections, the specific terms of which are set forth in clause (b)(iii) of the Emissions Annex, will govern the parties’ rights and obligations with respect to this Emissions Transaction. If none of the above options is selected, Option A(1) will apply.

Source.Contents:
/#
 Upon the occurrence of an Abandonment of Scheme, as defined in clause (h)(iv) of the Emissions Annex, one of the following elections, the specific terms of which are set forth in clause (b)(iii) of the Emissions Annex, will govern the parties’ rights and obligations with respect to this Emissions Transaction. If none of the above options is selected, Option A(1) will apply.
 #/
enum FpML5.confirmation.EnvironmentalAbandonmentOfSchemeEnum {
    # Abandonment of Scheme constitutes an Additional Termination Event.
    OptionA1 
    # Abandonment of Scheme entails no further obligations.
    OptionA2 
    # The applicability of Abandonment of Scheme to Emissions Transactions is set forth in the applicable Confirmation.
    OptionB 
    # The applicability of Abandonment of Scheme does not apply.
    OptionC 

}

OptionA1.Doc: Abandonment of Scheme constitutes an Additional Termination Event.
OptionA1.Name: OptionA1

OptionA2.Doc: Abandonment of Scheme entails no further obligations.
OptionA2.Name: OptionA2

OptionB.Doc: The applicability of Abandonment of Scheme to Emissions Transactions is set forth in the applicable Confirmation.
OptionB.Name: OptionB

OptionC.Doc: The applicability of Abandonment of Scheme does not apply.
OptionC.Name: OptionC
